                  </persName>
            . I made the iron-work of the cart, and know it to be Deadman's.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280703-45-person408">
                  JOHN 
                  BOWYER
               <interp inst="t18280703-45-person408" type="surname" value="BOWYER"></interp>
